---
import layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<layout lang="en">
	<main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-center">
		<h1 class="text-6xl font-black uppercase mb-10 tracking-tighter">About Dudes</h1>
		<div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 rounded-[40px] shadow-[10px_10px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] text-left space-y-6 text-xl">
			<p>
				We are a crew from **Bolzano, Italy**, who got tired of standard weather apps. 
				Temperature isn't just a number; it's a feeling, bro. 
			</p>
			<p>
				WeatherDude was built for those who want to look sharp and stay comfortable, 
				regardless of whether the forecast says it's "chilly" or "mild". 
				We build AI that understands **your** specific vibe.
			</p>
			<p class="font-bold underline decoration-lime-400 decoration-4">
				Join the movement. Dress smart. Stay authentic.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="mt-10">
			<a href="/en/" class="inline-block bg-black text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-lime-400 hover:text-black transition">Back to Home</a>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>